# R system config:

* put keys / passwords in users .Renviron file

* installing multiple R versions: https://support.rstudio.com/hc/en-us/articles/215488098-Installing-multiple-versions-of-R-on-Linux

* to change R version used by rstudio-server edit: sudo nano /etc/rstudio/rserver.conf

* to switch default blas: sudo update-alternatives --config libblas.so.3-x86_64-linux-gnu
* to switch default lappack: sudo update-alternatives --config liblapack.so.3-x86_64-linux-gnu
* use sessionInfo() in R to check blas / lapack version

------------------------------------------------





